    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin inserts quicktags of the admin page to the upper part of textarea of the comment form.</p>\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>You can edit tags in the admin page.</li>\n<li>You can limit quicktags by user roles.</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the extracted plugin folder and contained files to your /wp-content/plugins/ directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Navigate to Settings -&gt; Comment Form Quicktags</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.3.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed warning message.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added comments-popup.php support.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added escaping.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added French translations by Phenom.</li>\n<li>Fixed admin CSS.</li>\n<li>Fixed scripts for Mystique.</li>\n<li>Fixed script and style loading.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Russian translations by alex.</li>\n<li>Fixed CSS.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated Italian translations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added the role limitation option.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed a bug that comments.php of child themes wasn&#8217;t imported.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Italian translations by Gianni Diurno.</li>\n<li>Fixed a bug that the option form lost focus.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Made the priority of styles higher.</li>\n<li>Made scripts return &#8220;304 Not Modified&#8221;.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed a bug that plugin files weren&#8217;t loaded in WP2.6.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed a JSON library bug.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Finnish lang files by C. Hellberg.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Changed the document.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Implemented the admin page.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
